{"id":2119,"date":"2018-05-26T21:41:45","date_gmt":"2018-05-26T20:41:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?p=2119"},"modified":"2021-10-25T12:45:08","modified_gmt":"2021-10-25T11:45:08","slug":"unawatuna","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/unawatuna\/","title":{"rendered":"9 Unmissable Things To Do in Unawatuna, Sri Lanka"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">1. Unawatuna Beach<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The main beach at Unawatuna is popular with both tourists and locals. The wide stretched beaches offer some good swimming and a part of the beach is occupied with sunbeds to rent. On the west end of the beach, there is a little walk to a pagoda statue overlooking the bay.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The beach is directly connected to the city center with loads of little restaurants and bars. There is a great beach vibe going on here even after sunset.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-beaches\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Top 10 Paradise Beaches in Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg\" alt=\"things to do unawatuna sri lanka beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"305\" alt=\"things to do unawatuna sri lanka beach\" class=\"wp-image-7371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-600x406.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-450x305.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-800x542.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1080x731.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-266x180.jpg 266w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-768x520.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1024x693.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1440x975.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/imag