interest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154414\/things-to-do-unawatuna-pin-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154414\/things-to-do-unawatuna-pin-387x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Unmissable Things To Do in Unawatuna, Sri Lanka\" height=\"600\" width=\"387\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It is not as easy to visit as Unawatuna beach but worth the visit if you have time. It&#x2019;s about a 10-15 min drive from the center of Unawatuna town.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154256\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7460\" class=\"wp-image-7460 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154256\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154256\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154256\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154256\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154256\/things-to-do-unaw