na-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-local-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154259\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-local-1113x1440.jpg 1113w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154259\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-local-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154259\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-jungle-beach-local.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>4. Visit Galle Fort<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Galle Fort is something totally different in Sri Lanka. This great old fort is not filled with typical Sri Lankan architecture but&#xA0;has loads of influences of the Dutch, Portuguese and British. Galle Fort has loads of perfect souvenir shops and really great architecture. We love to wander around here for a full afternoon and watch the sunset on top of the fort wall.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/galle-fort\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Day Trip to Galle Fort<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n\n    <a class=\"ebook-banner ebook-banner--sl\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/shop\/ebooks\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" data-src=\"\/build\/images\/ebooks\/traveling-sri-lanka\/slebook-banner.jpg\" class=\"lazypreload\" height=\"225\" width=\"800\" alt=\"Ebook Sri Lanka\">\n    <\/a>\n    \n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>5. Surfing or Standup Paddleboard<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to get in the water? In between Unawatuna and Galle is a good beach to learn to surf. Note that the best season for surfing is between November and May. At Ahikava Surfschool, you can rent a board and maybe have some lessons as well. Grab a paddleboard during sunset, relax and just enjoy the moment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-surfing.jpg\" alt=\"things to do unawatuna sri lanka surfing\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"328\" alt=\"things to do unawatuna sri lanka surfing\" class=\"wp-image-7489 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154236\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-surfing.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154236\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-surfing-300x219.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154236\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-surfing-600x437.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154236\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-surfing-450x328.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\