49\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-450x305.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-800x543.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-1080x733.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-163x111.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-265x180.jpg 265w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-768x521.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-1024x695.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-1440x977.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154249\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-infinity-pool.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>8. Stay at Tri Lanka<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotel-tri\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Hotel Tri<\/a> is one of those hideaways near Unawatuna around Kogalla Lake. The sunrise and sunsets here are one of a kind overlooking the lake and cinnamon plantations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"277\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7487\" class=\"wp-image-7487 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1576px) 100vw, 1576px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2.jpg 1576w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-300x365.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-600x731.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-493x600.jpg 493w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-665x810.jpg 665w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-277x338.jpg 277w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-1261x1536.jpg 1261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154240\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-tri-lanka-2-25x30.jpg 25w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/