edspace_Kitchen-Unawatuna_Galle_Southern_Province.html\">Bedspace<\/a> (quite expensive but so good)<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g644047-d3641109-Reviews-Lemongrass_cafe-Unawatuna_Galle_Southern_Province.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lemongrass Cafe<\/a> (great place)<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g644047-d2427032-Reviews-Happy_Spice-Unawatuna_Galle_Southern_Province.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Happy Spice<\/a> (cheap and local)<\/li><li>SkinnyTom&#x2019;s Deli (best breakfast)<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7366\" class=\"wp-image-7366 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154439\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-breakfast-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.c